'''2010年[[MTV音樂錄影帶大獎|MTV音樂錄影帶大獎]]'''于2010年9月12日在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]{{tsl|en|Nokia Theatre L.A. Live|微软剧院|诺基亚剧院}}举办，以嘉獎前一年的最優秀的[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]。本届音乐录像带大奖由{{tsl|en|Chelsea Handler||切尔西·汉德勒}}主持，是16年来第一位主持该奖项的女主持。<ref name="host">[http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1646050/20100819/story.jhtml Chelsea Handler To Host The 2010 MTV Video Music Awards | MTV Video Music Awards] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1646050/20100819/story.jhtml |date=20100923224029 }}. Mtv.com (2010-08-19). Retrieved on 2013-08-25.</ref>

[[Lady_Gaga|Lady Gaga]]在这一年被提名13次，是MTV音樂錄影帶大獎历史上单年被提名最多的女艺人。其中，她的歌曲《[[罗曼死|Bad Romance]]》和《[[電話_(歌曲)|Telephone]]》同时入圍了{{tsl|en|MTV Video Music Award for Video of the Year|MTV年度音樂錄影帶大獎|年度音樂錄影帶大獎}}。<ref>{{cite web| title= Lady Gaga's 13 VMA Nominations: How Do They Measure Up?| first= Gil| last= Kaufman| publisher= [[MTV_Networks|MTV Networks]]| url= http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1644983/20100803/lady_gaga.jhtml| date= 2010-08-03| accessdate= 2010-09-18| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100905062626/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1644983/20100803/lady_gaga.jhtml| archivedate= 2010-09-05| deadurl= no}}</ref>此外，她也是当晚最大赢家，《Telephone》赢得了最佳合作奖，《Bad Romance》赢得了7个奖项，包括年度音樂錄影帶大獎，使她收获了8个太空人雕像。在领取年度音樂錄影帶大獎时，她公布了自己第2张录音室专辑的名称“[[Born_This_Way_(专辑)|Born This Way]]”，并清唱了[[天生完美_(歌曲)|同名歌曲]]的片段。<ref>{{cite web| title= Lady Gaga Names Her New Album ‘Born This Way’| first= Daniel| last= Kreps| publisher= Rolling Stone| url= http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/17386/202983| date= 2010-09-13| accessdate= 2010-09-13| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100916021243/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/17386/202983| archivedate= 2010-09-16| deadurl= no}}</ref>在领奖时，Lady Gaga以[[生牛肉装|完全由生牛肉制成的帽子、钱包和鞋子]]装扮自己，引发了[[善待动物组织|善待动物组织]]的强烈批评。<ref name="Newkirk">{{cite web| title= Lady Gaga's Meat Dress| first= Ingrid| last= Newkirk| publisher= [[善待动物组织|PETA]]| url= http://blog.peta.org/archives/2010/09/lady_gaga_meat_dress.php| date= 2010-09-13| accessdate= 2010-09-13| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100915034058/http://blog.peta.org/archives/2010/09/lady_gaga_meat_dress.php| archivedate= 2010-09-15| deadurl= yes}}</ref><ref name="Vena">{{cite web| title= Lady Gaga Meat Dress Draws Criticism From PETA| first= Jocelyn| last= Vena| publisher= [[MTV_Networks|MTV Networks]]| url= http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1647732/20100913/lady_gaga.jhtml| date= 2010-09-13| accessdate= 2010-09-13| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100914201956/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1647732/20100913/lady_gaga.jhtml| archivedate= 2010-09-14| deadurl= no}}</ref>

本屆音樂錄影帶大獎颁奖典礼总计吸引了1140万观众收视率，是继{{tsl|en|2002 MTV Video Music Awards|2002年MTV音樂錄影帶大獎|2002年}}以来收视人数最多的一届颁奖典礼。<ref>Carter, Kelley L.. (2010-09-13) [http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1647778/20100913/story.jhtml 2010 VMAs Nab MTV's Biggest Ratings Since 2002 | MTV Video Music Awards] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1647778/20100913/story.jhtml |date=20101120220023 }}. Mtv.com. Retrieved on 2013-08-25.</ref>

